Shiinaha: TCM waxaa loo isticmaalay Shiinaha kun sano si loo daaweeyo cuduro kala duwan.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, saameynteeda waxay ku xiran tahay isku darka maaddooyinka kala duwan ee lagu daro daawo, taas oo ku kala duwanaan doonta iyadoo ku xiran sida loo ogaado cudurka, iyadoo lagu saleynayo mabaadi'da TCM.
Qaybaha ugu waxtarka badan ayaa la garan waayay ama ma jiraan wax macluumaad ah oo sax ah oo ku saabsan qaybahaas ama isku darkooda ugu fiican oo ay adagtahay in la kala saaro lana xaqiijiyo.
Ma jiro daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo COVID-19 ah, TCM waxay noqotay mid ka mid ah hababka ugu caansan ee lagu daaweeyo bukaannada qaba calaamadaha fudud ilaa dhexdhexaadka ah ama kuwa ka soo kabashada xaaladaha daran.
Tusaale ahaan, kaabsoosha Shu Feng Jie Du iyo Lian Hua Qing Wen ayaa lagu ogaadey inay waxtar u leeyihiin daaweynta COVID-19.
Heerka ugu sarreeya ee ka soo kabashada bukaanada COVID-19 waxaa lagu arkay gobollo badan oo Shiinaha ah, oo ay ku jiraan Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) iyo Hunan (50%), kuwaas oo 87% bukaanadooda ay isticmaaleen TCM, halka heerka ugu hooseeya (13%) uu ku dhacay gobolka Hubei, oo kaliya 30% bukaanada COVID-19 ay isticmaaleen TCM.
