Cilmi-baarista aan caadiga ahayn: C-reactive protein (CRP) ee dhiigga ayaa muujinaya culeyska caabuqa ama dhaawaca unugyada waxaana loo soo jeediyay inay noqoto mid ka mid ah waxyaabaha laga yaabo inay ka hortagaan xaaladda cudurka, jawaabta daaweynta iyo soo kabashada kama dambaysta ah.
Xidhiidhka u dhexeeya xasaasiyadda COVID-19, falanqaynta xaaladda cudurka iyo heerarka CRP ayaa sidoo kale la soo jeediyay.
Waxaa intaa dheer, heerarka sareeya ee lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) iyo creatine kinase (CK) ayaa sidoo kale ka caawin kara saadaalinta natiijada.
Enzymes-ka waxaa laga helaa qaybo badan oo jidhka ah, gaar ahaan wadnaha iyo beerka, waxaana la soo saaraa inta lagu jiro burburka unugyada.
