Dukaamada Australia ayaa hoos u dhigay xadka kaararka musqusha ee hal mar la iibsan karo.
Dukaamada Australia ee Woolworths iyo Coles ayaa xaddiday waraaqaha musqusha ee ay ku iibsanayaan dukaamada qaranka oo dhan hal iyo laba baakadood.
Isniintii, ALDI waxay sidoo kale bilawday inay soo bandhigto xaddidaadda iibinta hal xirmo oo keliya qofkiiba.
Xayiraadaha ayaa lagu soo bandhigay bogagga shabakadda Facebook ee shirkadaha alaabada iyo fariimaha.
Waxaa la sheegay in iibsadayaashu ay keydsanayaan alaabada ay u baahan yihiin, iyadoo cabsida COVID-19 ay sababtay in la go'doomiyo.
Arbacadii, Woolworths waxay sidoo kale ku xaddiday iibsiga waraaqaha musqusha inay ku iibsadaan hal xirmo amar kasta oo loogu talagalay gaarsiinta guriga.
Isbedelkan ayaa la raacayaa xaddidaadda iibinta afar nooc hal mar oo ay bilaabeen Woolworths iyo Coles 4 iyo 5 Maarso.
Coles ayaa wargeyskeeda 8-da Maarso ku sheegtay in dukaamo badan oo ay ku jiraan afar alaab oo qof walba lagu iibiyo ay wali ku jiraan alaab la iibinayo saacad gudaheed, iyadoo u adeegsaneysa dalabka "aan la arag", laakiin ALDI waxay ku sheegtay Facebook post inay ugu yeertay dalabka "aan la filayn".
Afhayeenka shirkadda Woolworths ayaa sheegay in iibka uu si lama filaan ah kor ugu kacay todobaadkii hore.
Dukaanka Kosko ee magaalada Kimbra ayaa toddobaadkii hore xaddiday tirada la ogol yahay ee laba duub.
Si loo yareeyo yaraanta alaabada, Coles waxay amarro badan ka bixisay alaab-qeybiyeyaasha wax soo saarka waxayna kordhisay maraakiibta dhowr jeer. Woolworths waxay iibsatay alaab dheeri ah si ay u hubiso in alaabtu ay hore u hesho maalmaha Arbacada ee loo qoondeeyay ALDI.
Russell Zinnemann, oo ah agaasimaha fulinta ee Ururka Ganacsatada Australia ayaa sheegay in ganacsatada ay rabaan inay kordhiyaan keydka alaabada, laakiin ay ku adkeynayaan in ay xaddidaan waqtiga ay gaariga ku imaan karaan maamulka deegaanka.
Waxa uu sheegay in alaab-qeybiyeyaashu ay isku dayayaan inay buuxiyaan baahida, iyo in ay jiraan arrimo yaryar oo gaar ah, taas oo keeneysa in kharashka wax soo saarka uu kor u kaco.
