Dr. Gary Mortimer oo ah khabiir ku takhasusay tafaariiqda oo ka tirsan jaamacadda tiknoolajiyadda Queensland ayaa ku warramay wargeyska News.com.au in dukaamada wax lagu iibiyo ay buuxiyaan alaabada habeen kasta.
Wuxuu faallo ka bixiyay in waraaqaha musqusha uu yahay mid qaata meel, oo kaliya tiro yar ayaa lagu keydin karaa, oo marka la iibiyo, meelo badan oo bannaan ayaa ku haray goobta, sidaa darteed yaraanta waraaqaha musqusha ayaa dadka ka dhigeysa kuwo aan raaxo lahayn.
