Shirkadda Who Gives a Crap, oo iibisa waraaqaha musqusha dib loo warshadeeyay, ayaa sheegtay Arbacadii in ay ka dhamaanayaan alaabtii ay isticmaali jireen.
Wararka News.com.au ayaa sheegaya in shirkadaha Kimball Clock, oo soo saara warqadda musqusha ee Kleenex, iyo Solaris, oo soo saara Sorben, ay si adag u shaqeeyaan 24 saacadood toddobaadkiiba si ay u sii wadaan bixinta.
