Sida laga soo xigtay warbixinta ABC Australia ee 3-da Maarso, dukaamada ayaa markii hore ka gaabsaday inay xaddido, waxayna sheegeen inaysan qorsheyneynin inay xaddido iibsadayaasha.
Russell Zimmerman ayaa intaas ku daray in dalabka badeecadaha kale uu kor u kacay, oo ay ku jiraan waji-xidhka, nadiifiyeyaasha, qalabka qalajiyaha, gacmo-dhaqaajinta iyo burka.
