Dr. Zhang Jixian ayaa laga helay cudurka sambabada ee aan la ogeyn sababta 26ka Diseembar, isla markiiba markii la ogaaday, waxay 27kii Diseembar u wargelisay Wuhan Jainghan CDC oo ka socota isbitaalkeeda.
Baaritaanka asalka ah ee baaritaanka asalka ah ee 27 Diseembar 2019, ayaa lagu ogaaday jiritaanka coronavirus-ka oo la mid ah SARS.
