Agaasimaha guud ee WHO Tedros Edhanhuang ayaa sheegay in bayaanka PHEIC uu yahay mid "xasaasi ah, gaar ahaan sababtoo ah khatarta faafitaanka caalamiga ah ee dalalka dakhligoodu hooseeyo iyo kuwa dakhligoodu dhexdhexaad yahay oo aan lahayn nidaam caafimaad oo adag".
Tedros ayaa ka jawaabay xayiraadaha safarka isagoo sheegay in aysan jirin sabab loo qaato tallaabooyin faragelin aan loo baahnayn ku sameyn kara safarka caalamiga ah iyo ganacsiga, isagoo sheegay in WHO aysan ku talineynin xannibaadaha ganacsiga iyo safarka.
5-tii Febraayo, WHO ayaa bulshada caalamka ka codsatay in ay ku darto $675 milyan oo doollar si ay u maalgeliso diyaar garowga istiraatiijiyadeed ee wadamada dakhligoodu hooseeyo.
Tedros ayaa soo saaray bayaan uu ku sheegay "Waxaan awood u leenahay kaliya inta ugu daciifsan ee aan awood u leenahay" wuxuuna ku booriyay bulshada caalamiga ah "In maanta maalgashadaan, haddii kale qiimaha ayaa ka weyn". Shir jaraa'id oo uu qabtay 11ka Febraayo, WHO ayaa magaca cudurka ku bixisay COVID-19.
