Kooxda khubarada ayaa sheegtay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay inuu helo faragelin badbaadin ah, taasina ay mas'uul ka tahay dowladda.
Ururku wuxuu carrabka ku adkeeyay in la'aanta ilaha ama caymiska caafimaadka aysan marnaba noqon karin sabab lagu takooro koox gaar ah.
Khubarada ayaa carrabka ku adkeeyay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay daryeel caafimaad, oo ay ku jiraan dadka naafada ah iyo kuwa ka tirsan qowmiyadaha laga tirada badan yahay, dadka waayeelka ah, qaxootiga hoy la'aanta gudaha, dadka hoy la'aanta ah, dadka ku nool saboolnimada, dadka la haysto, laakiin sidoo kale qaxootiga iyo kooxaha aan la aqoonsan ee u baahan taageerada dowladda.
