Nadiifiyaha gacmaha ama sunta gacmaha waa biyo ku saleysan nadiifiye gacmeed.
1990s iyo bilowgii qarnigii 21aad, gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha ee aan ku saleysanayn aalkolada (oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha, gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha, ama nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha) ayaa noqday kuwa ugu caansan.
Inta badan waxaa loo qaabeeyey cabbomer (polymer acrylic acid) oo ah isopropyl alcohol ama ethanol oo ah wakiilo dhalaalaya, gel ahaan ama dareere ahaan iyadoo la adeegsanayo humidifier sida glycerin, ama budo ahaan si loo fududeeyo isticmaalka loona yareeyo saameynta qalajinta ee khamriga.
Ku darista hydrogen peroxide oo daciif ah ayaa sii kordhisa waxqabadka ka hortagga bakteeriyada. Qalabka lagu nadiifiyo gacmaha oo leh ugu yaraan 60 ilaa 95% khamri ayaa waxtar u leh dilka bakteeriyada.
Nadiifiyeyaasha saafiga ah ee khamriga ayaa dilaya bakteeriyada, bakteeriyada daawooyinka badan (MRSA iyo VRE), TB, iyo fayrasyada qaarkood (oo ay ku jiraan HIV, RAS, RSV, rhinovirus, hepatitis, TB, iyo hepatitis).
70% khamriga ku jirta saabuun gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha ayaa 99.97% bakteeriyada gacmaha ku dilaya 30 ilbiriqsi ka dib marka la maydho (3.5 hoos u dhac ama 35 decibel) iyo 1 daqiiqo ka dib marka la maydho 99.99% ilaa 99.999% (4 ilaa 5 hoos u dhac). Saafiyada gacmaha ayaa ugu waxtarka badan bakteeriyada, laakiin waxtar yar fayrasyada qaarkood.
Qalabka lagu nadiifiyo gacmaha ee ku saleysan aalkolada ayaa u dhow in aan waxyeello u geysan fayrasyada Norovirus ama Norvov, kuwaas oo keena xanuunka ugu badan ee caloosha iyo mindhicirka. Isku shaandheynta waxaa loo isticmaalaa gacmaha oo leh wax lagu nadiifiyo gacmaha ama aalkolada ku filan si loo hubiyo in labada gacmood ay qoyaan yihiin ama nadiif yihiin.
Labada dhinac ee hore iyo kan dambe ee gacmaha iyo inta u dhaxaysa iyo faraha faraha oo dhan waxaa lagu masaxaa ilaa ay qalalaan, caadi ahaan 30 ilbiriqsi.
